params.sqlcmd: "select " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_INST_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ITEM_CD, " +" to_char(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_INST_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ISSUE_INST_QTY\\", " +" to_char(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"TOTAL_ISSUE_QTY\\", " +" to_char(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.W_SHIP_REMAIN_QTY, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"W_SHIP_REMAIN_QTY\\", " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.SCDL_ISSUE_DATE) as \\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\", " +" FncGetFormattedDatetime(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_CMPLT_DATE) as \\"ISSUE_CMPLT_DATE\\", " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_CMPLT_FLG, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_TYP, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.WH_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.WS_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.WORK_ODR_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.WORK_IN_PROC_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.PUCH_ODR_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.VEND_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.CONS_TYP, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.OD_NO, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.PS_EDITION, " +" to_char(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_INST_UNIT_DENOMINATOR, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ISSUE_INST_UNIT_DENOMINATOR\\", " +" to_char(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_INST_UNIT_NUMERATOR, 'FM999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ISSUE_INST_UNIT_NUMERATOR\\", " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ISSUE_INST_COMMENT, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.JOB_ODR_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.ITEM_NAME, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.WH_NAME, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.WS_NAME, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.VEND_ANAME, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.PROC_NAME, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.OPR_INST_CD_ITEM, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.OPR_INST_CD_PROC, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.PLANT_CD, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STOCK_UNIT, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.MRP_ODR_TYP, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.JOB_ODR_DETAIL_NO, " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.LOT_CTRL_FLG " +"from " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST " +"where " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"WS_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"VEND_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" like ? " +" and((V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" >= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI')) " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI')) " +" and(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"OPR_INST_CD_ITEM\\" like ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"OPR_INST_CD_PROC\\" like ?) " +" and(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ?) " +" AND V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"WH_CD\\" like ? " +" AND V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" like ? " +" AND(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = ?) " +" AND V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_INST_ISS_FLG\\" = ? " +"order by " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\""
"select " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" M_WS.\\"WS_NAME\\" as \\"WS_NAME\\", " +" M_WS.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_WS " +"where " +" M_WS.\\"WS_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_NAME\\" as \\"VEND_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_VEND_CTRL " +"where " +" M_VEND_CTRL.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ( " +" SELECT " +" COMPANY_CD " +" FROM " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +" WHERE " +" CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" ) " +" and M_VEND_CTRL.\\"VEND_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_OPR_INST_SLIP.\\"OPR_INST_CD\\" as \\"OPR_INST_CD\\", " +" T_OPR_INST_SLIP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_OPR_INST_SLIP.\\"OPR_INST_CD_GNR_TYP\\" as \\"OPR_INST_CD_GNR_TYP\\" " +"from " +" T_OPR_INST_SLIP " +"where " +" T_OPR_INST_SLIP.\\"OPR_INST_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" as \\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR " +"where " +" T_RLSD_PUCH_ODR.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" as \\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\", " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\" " +"from " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"where " +" T_ISSUE_INST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" COUNT(1) " +"from " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST " +"where " +" V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"WS_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"VEND_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"PUCH_ODR_CD\\" like ? " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_INST_CD\\" like ? " +" and((V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" >= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" and V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" <= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI')) " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI') " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"SCDL_ISSUE_DATE\\" = TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI')) " +" and(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"OPR_INST_CD_ITEM\\" like ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"OPR_INST_CD_PROC\\" like ?) " +" and(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.STATUS = ?) " +" AND V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"WH_CD\\" like ? " +" AND V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" like ? " +" AND(V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = ? " +" or V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_TYP\\" = ?) " +" AND V_WORK_ISSUE_INST_LST.\\"ISSUE_INST_ISS_FLG\\" = ? " +" AND ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"select " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.WH_CD, " +" M_WH.WH_NAME " +"from " +" M_WH_PRIORITY, " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.WH_CD = M_WH.WH_CD " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_WH_PRIORITY.ITEM_CD = ? " +" and M_WH.MRP_FLG = ? " +"order by " +" M_WH_PRIORITY.WH_PRIORITY_REF_NO ASC"
"select " +" M_WH.WH_CD, " +" M_WH.WH_NAME " +"from " +" M_WH " +"where " +" M_WH.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_WH.MRP_FLG = ? " +"order by " +" M_WH.WH_CD ASC"
"SELECT " +" ISSUE_INST_CD " +"FROM " +" T_ISSUE_INST " +"WHERE " +" ISSUE_INST_CD = ? " +"AND ISSUE_INST_ISS_FLG <> 1 " +"FOR UPDATE NOWAIT"
